Thank you very much for the upload.  Any chance we can get a hold of the new 8th ed solution manual? the 7th edition solutions posted here on TPB seems to have all different problems.
Thank you so much for this!

@tymzn32  Solution manuals are always crap shots. But if I read you right you have one fully worked problem set (7th) for study and a second set with final answers (8th) for genuine practice (the 7th set serving as a guide) and mastering of the subject. The best of both worlds, eh? Previous exam questions solved in an exam setting (timed, closed books) for final prep. Ya betta be good...
